hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 四维速度和四维加速度的定义  
   $$U^\mu = \frac{dx^\mu}{d\tau} = (\gamma c,\;\gamma v^i),$$  
   $$A^\mu = \frac{dU^\mu}{d\tau} = \gamma\,\frac{dU^\mu}{dt}.$$

2. 四维加速度的时间分量  
   $$\frac{dU^0}{dt} = \frac{d(\gamma c)}{dt}
     = c\,\frac{d\gamma}{dt},\quad
     \frac{d\gamma}{dt}=\gamma^3\frac{\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}}{c^2}  
     \;\Longrightarrow\;
     \frac{dU^0}{dt}=\gamma^3\frac{\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}}{c}$$  
   $$\implies A^0 = \gamma\,\frac{dU^0}{dt}
     = \gamma^4\frac{\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}}{c}.$$

3. 四维加速度的空间分量  
   $$\frac{dU^i}{dt}
     = \frac{d(\gamma v^i)}{dt}
     = \gamma\,a^i + v^i\,\frac{d\gamma}{dt}
     = \gamma\,a^i + \gamma^3\frac{\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}}{c^2}v^i$$  
   $$\implies A^i = \gamma\frac{dU^i}{dt}
     = \gamma^2\,a^i + \gamma^4\frac{\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}}{c^2}v^i.$$

4. 特殊情况 $\vec{v}\cdot \vec{a}=0$  
   $$A^0=0,\qquad A^i=\gamma^2\,a^i.$$

5. 固有加速度的大小  
   $$A_\mu A^\mu = (A^0)^2 - \delta_{ij}A^iA^j
     = -\gamma^4\,a^2
     \;\Longrightarrow\;
     a_0 = \sqrt{-A_\mu A^\mu} = \gamma^2\,a.$$
